Simple and full backup Git repositories


Simple start. Easy config. Detailed log.
Auto Clone/Update repository (full and incremental backup).
Backup all or manual branches. Pack repository. Auto and manual choise compressor.
Circular buffer for archives (default disabled).


1) Get this: git clone git://github.com/progman/git_backup.git
2) View and run git_backup_example.sh for simple start
3) Just use it!
